message.content: San Francisco offers a variety of tourist attractions that cater to different interests. Some popular attractions include Fisherman's Wharf, where you can enjoy fresh seafood, visit the famous Pier 39, and take a boat tour to Alcatraz Island. Lombard Street, known as the "crookedest street in the world," is another must-see spot, with its winding and picturesque road.
